{
  "tool": "search_files",
  "args": {
    "query": "vacation plans Hawaii"
  }
}
{
  "tool": "query_llm",
  "args": {
    "prompt": "Here is the JSON result from searching files for \"vacation plans Hawaii\": <tool_result_0/>. From this data, find the activity scheduled for June 13. Provide a concise description of the activity."
  }
}
{
  "tool": "query_llm",
  "args": {
    "prompt": "Here is the JSON result from searching files for \"vacation plans Hawaii\": <tool_result_0/>. Extract the packing list for the Hawaii vacation from this document. Provide the packing list items as a bullet list, one item per line."
  }
}
{
  "tool": "create_file",
  "args": {
    "filename": "hawaii-packing-list.docx",
    "content": "<tool_result_2/>"
  }
}
{
  "tool": "query_llm",
  "args": {
    "prompt": "Extract the file_id from the following JSON: <tool_result_3/>. Respond with only the file_id string."
  }
}
{
  "tool": "share_file",
  "args": {
    "email": "john.doe@gmail.com",
    "file_id": "<tool_result_4/>",
    "permission": "read"
  }
}

On June 13, according to the vacation plan, we will <tool_result_1/>. The packing list has been saved to "hawaii-packing-list.docx" and shared with john.doe@gmail.com with read permissions.
